<p><b>Hans Ledwinka</b> (14 February 1878 – 2 March 1967) was an <a href="/wiki/Austria" title="Austria">Austrian</a> <a href="/wiki/Automobile" title="Automobile" class="mw-redirect">automobile</a> designer.</p>
<p></p>
